/Damageinfo/

# User-specific runtime data — the userdata/ root (prefs, settings, profiles,
# custom-buff deltas, OTA content cache) is created fresh at runtime next to the
# exe; never commit it. settings/ + profiles/ are the pre-overhaul locations.
userdata/
settings/*.json
profiles/*.json
logs/

# IDE / dev tooling
.vscode/
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
help_tab_text.txt
